disease_details.name: __Bacterial_spot
disease_details.symptoms: ['Small brown spots on leaves', 'Spots turn black or fall out', 'Fruit develops deep cracks', 'Defoliation']
disease_details.treatment: Apply copper-based bactericides every 7-10 days during wet periods. Maintain good air circulation and prune infected branches.

disease_details.name: __Apple_scab
disease_details.symptoms: ['Dark, sunken lesions on leaves', 'Lesions on fruit and stems']
disease_details.treatment: Apply fungicides and remove infected leaves
